58:31.246 --> 58:33.422
-Mondays and Saturdays.
-Mm-hmm.

58:33.553 --> 58:36.338
It's a good thing I come back
to see them Saturday, then.

58:39.777 --> 58:41.082
Where you from?

58:41.866 --> 58:43.128
Cuba.

58:44.608 --> 58:46.914
Cuba.

58:46.958 --> 58:48.307
Nice.

58:50.396 --> 58:53.094
I had a great time in Havana,
a long time ago.

58:54.574 --> 58:55.706
You did?

58:56.968 --> 58:59.100
Yeah. Yep.

59:00.667 --> 59:05.933
I went down there
for a music program.

59:05.977 --> 59:07.413
Spent a couple of months,

59:07.456 --> 59:11.112
and had the, uh, full
Cuban experience.

59:12.200 --> 59:19.164
You know, food, music, people.

59:19.294 --> 59:20.557
Man, I love that place.

59:23.429 --> 59:27.564
