1:07:31.830 --> 1:07:32.918
Leave.

1:07:36.704 --> 1:07:39.011
Get the fuck outta here!

1:07:39.055 --> 1:07:40.534
[saxophone stops playing]

1:07:40.665 --> 1:07:42.232
[woman] Is everything okay, Jim?

1:07:42.275 --> 1:07:44.277
It's fine. It's fine. Fine.

1:07:46.105 --> 1:07:48.151
My friend Nico is...
