1:09:06.228 --> 1:09:07.969
So I don't wanna see you
in my park.

1:09:08.013 --> 1:09:10.450
You understand?
I run these parks.

1:09:10.537 --> 1:09:12.583
I own these benches,
and if you ain't paying me rent,

1:09:12.670 --> 1:09:14.149
I don't wanna see
your face here.

1:09:14.193 --> 1:09:16.934
-You understand me?
-I do. Yeah.

1:09:17.457 --> 1:09:20.156
I'm leaving right now, okay?

1:09:20.199 --> 1:09:21.505
I'm leaving.

1:09:27.946 --> 1:09:30.166
[sighs]

1:09:31.210 --> 1:09:35.171
I'm leaving. Just leave me
right now. I'm leaving.

1:09:35.258 --> 1:09:38.174
Leaving. Easy.

1:09:38.261 --> 1:09:40.785
We're cool. Right?

1:09:40.827 --> 1:09:43.221
-Are we?
-We're not cool.

1:09:43.265 --> 1:09:45.005
We're cool.
I mean, I'm leaving right now.

1:09:45.050 --> 1:09:47.051
It's your park. The bench.

1:09:47.183 --> 1:09:48.532
That's fine.

1:09:52.797 --> 1:09:55.495
