working in Europe.

1:10:17.255 --> 1:10:18.388
Who cares?

1:10:21.434 --> 1:10:24.611
What's up with this guy?

1:10:24.655 --> 1:10:26.526
Well, do something!
Tell someone.

1:10:26.570 --> 1:10:28.398
Yeah.

1:10:35.666 --> 1:10:37.842
Sorry, but you gotta leave.

1:10:37.885 --> 1:10:39.583
Yeah, man. Sorry about that.

1:10:40.975 --> 1:10:43.021
[soft piano music playing]

1:11:52.395 --> 1:11:53.570
Hold on.

1:11:53.700 --> 1:11:54.919
-How's your coffee?
-Good.

1:11:54.962 --> 1:11:56.573
-Okay. Milk?
-Yes.

1:11:56.702 --> 1:11:57.922
You got a call.

1:12:00.098 --> 1:12:01.186
[sighs]

1:12:04.362 --> 1:12:06.234
